_sText:
This map based my unreleased cs 1.6 map.
Source versions only have one bomb site. (Full version 1.6 map coming soon.)


Background story:
Kurdistan builds a water intake on the mountains and plans to build a pipe to Iraq. As an equivalent, Iraq offers weapons of mass destruction. Iran's ultranationalist faction doesn't appreciate these actions and now terrorists and a commando group fighting in the name of USA's forces encounter in the water intake's construction site.
